---
title: Double Chorizo Patatas Bravas with Baby Plum Tomatoes, Rocket and Garlic Aioli
description: This Double Chorizo Patatas Bravas is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R10_W17_UK_R21243-2_Main__4low-bff21219.jpg
